Super Maths is a game designed to help players improve their mental math skills. It provides the player with math problems of varying difficulties, which the player must solve within an allotted time, while also being distracted by various disturbances (flashing colors, obnoxious music, popup messages, etc).

Conceived by Stephen Picone in 2010.
Development began in June 2013.
As of June 14, 2014, Stephen Picone is the sole developer.

This project is open source.